OL,3,CWorkers putting in billions of pounds
OL,4,Cof unpaid overtime ` report
OL,6,FWorkers put in #31 billion worth of
OL,7,Funpaid overtime last year, with
OL,8,Fteachers and health and care managers
OL,9,Fworking the longest hours for free,
OL,10,Fresearch suggests.
OL,12,FThe TUC urged people to work their
OL,13,Fproper hours and take breaks and
OL,14,Fencouraged managers to set reasonable
OL,15,Fworkloads.
OL,17,FThe union organisation dubbed Friday
OL,18,FWork Your Proper Hours Day to
OL,19,Fhighlight the cost to workers of doing
OL,20,Fso much unpaid overtime.
