OL,3,CWorkers putting in billions of pounds
OL,4,Cof unpaid overtime ` report
OL,6,FThe TUC said government plans to
OL,7,Frecruit 6,500 additional teachers will
OL,8,Fhelp to improve levels of work
OL,9,Fintensity, more engagement was needed
OL,10,Fon workforce issues across the public
OL,11,Fsector.
OL,13,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,14,F"Most workers don't mind putting in
OL,15,Fextra hours from time to time, but
OL,16,Fthey should be paid for it.
OL,18,F"This analysis shows once again the
OL,19,Fstaffing pressures in our public
OL,20,Fservices that have been driven by 14
OL,21,Fyears of Tory mismanagement.
